	Two pkgs type
		RPM and Debian packages are most common
		Name of pkgs mostly same
		"apt-get"  and "dpkg"  for Debian (like Ubuntu)
		"yum" and "rpm" with RPM packages (like Redhat)

	Performance related pkgs are
		gnome-system-monitor
		sysstat   -->  cifsiostat, iostat, mpstat, nfsiostat-sysstat, pidstat, sar (system activity report)
		procps-ng	 
			--> free, pmap, ps, slabtop, snice, top, uptime, vmstat, watch, tload	
